Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:31.27,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The three of us should start a company together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea. \N-What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Dream Crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:27.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:29.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kumamoto-san, Ushiroda-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I'm able to welcome you as our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:34.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can understand this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't hate it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:54.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There was nothing like this in my old job, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:55.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I personally think it's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:00.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Was it a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:12.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't ask something that's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:14.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a waste if we don't eat the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:26.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't force an adult to act like students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:28.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that welcome equals party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:31.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't fire off crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys feel any danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are we in a tough spot after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At this rate, nobody will invest in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a Unicorn company, with the speed of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:51.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, you have to evolve with the speed of Neutrino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean...\N-That's a networking party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:56.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because various investors will attend the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so you guys may get the chance to meet someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that will able to grow your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That person always disappears after he says a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:16.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely grab that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So this is a networking party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:37.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I try, they always went to grab a drink and never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Simply put, I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san. \N-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that you also come to this kind of place, Shirakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's a young entrepreneur who's company is the closest to being called a Unicorn company in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He was a member of Dog Run's first class if I remember correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:03.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So, I wonder if we can exchange business cards with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people surrounding him though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We've got nothing to lose. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Shirakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're from Dream Crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Darn it, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai Riko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the weird question, but did you go Aoba Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh? That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was the leader of the commute group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Satoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He was in sixth grade when I was in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I remember you because you always took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You've always been a fast walker, right Satoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:14.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The app allows users to check information on registered products in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san really became our adviser...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When someone asked you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:27.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please lead us to become an Unicorn company!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really busy nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, please, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together now.\N-Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:43.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,DreCra is going to be big in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Be careful with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In other words, Nokoruna's main revenue comes from the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The commission from supermarkets and stores. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:57.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll get straight to the point, at this rate, Nokuruna won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nokoruna won't survive... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The idea of sharing the leftover meals from supermarkets is interesting, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the problem is that there is no development of service or major growth strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What if a similar service comes along later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They'll come and fight for our market share.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About developing a service for the future, I want you to think about it concretely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,100 suggestions to start. \N-100 suggestions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If your aim is to become an Unicorn company, \Nyou have to grow faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's really a fast walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Make Nokoruna available in food courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Number 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Food stalls during festivals. \N-It's already on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Or rather this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They're being pushed around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, it's no use for me to think about that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:05.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that we as adults should give them some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was also in the Financial Planning Department of Mitsubashi Bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so I have a lot of ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:23.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,100, a service to buy leftover lunch boxes from TV drama shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I still can't see a big growth potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of similar ideas.\N-You told us to came up with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:37.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, what if we look at our connections with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,supermarkets and retailers as a sales channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by sales channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:45.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to have them stock Nokoruna branded items and sell them on participating stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You mean that Nokoruna will create something that will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Something that will last...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Frozen foods that will be okay even if it's unsold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Frozen foods sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll invest, so do you want to do it together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The company can't grow if you only doing things that you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Leaving Dog Run without getting any investment is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My hope is to avoid being pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's proceed with the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Become an adult, Riko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I haven't said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you. \N-He's really a fast walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:26.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,DreCra, I heard that you're teaming up with Shirakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard the footsteps of an Unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko haven't said that she's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? This is a chance of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,According to my data, 90% of all startups goes bankrupt in 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't become a mass production type company and exit in mediocrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's also a pattern where he leaves before saying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not Nokoruna if we sell something that lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's for the growth of the company. Are you a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not comfortable with it. If that's the case then there's no meaning of the three of us starting a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If we go under, then it will be really meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Riko? \N-Which one of us is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it me, Shinji?\N-Is it me, Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which one of us do you choose? \N-Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is all going too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When you have to make a choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,how do you make that choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:40.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you're saying, but you don't look cute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that I can't decide on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Making decisions is our job as presidents, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be in a zen like state...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:40.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san. I see that you've come to like plastic models now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be in a zen like state again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to exorcise it?\N-Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:55.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was pressed by the two people that I started the company with to choose between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:59.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A love triangle, huh? I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:01.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's tingling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Speaking of love triangles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:16.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,, The Macross series, which began with \N"The Super Dimension Fortress Macross",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:24.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,is characterized by it's unique sense of science fiction that combines three elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,high-speed mecha action of the Variable Fighters, songs, and love triangles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's been going for more than 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:35.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Among them, people said that Macross Plus is unlike the usual robot anime, more like a trendy TV dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,With the songs of Sharon Apple playing in the background,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,a too painful love triangle or the fight with AI,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and the famous scene called "The Legendary 5 Seconds",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,this is a legendary masterpiece that has not faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are three figures inside of the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, it's even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This Macross, transforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:12.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The YF-19 is an experimental Variable Fighter presented by Shinsei Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,for Project Super Nova to determine the next generation of Variable Fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are many different colored parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Also known as colored plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the past, it was only possible to create one runner with same color, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:32.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,over the years, it's now possible to create one runner with different colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's fascinating, even before you build it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The parts are so detailed that I want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It feels like excitement similar to the factory excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, it's just right for me to get in a zen like state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go according to the manual first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The face is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:31.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You get attached the first time you see it's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can hear the sound of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Click... What a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can hear it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Click...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a low-grade tea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:22.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I haven't had tea recently, it hits the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, it's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel great, the tiredness is comparable to climbing a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Like climbing Mt. Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A painting booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can paint parts with the color of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:01.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The depth of the world of painting is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I'm scared of the infinite obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We also have paint brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's go on a little detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:30.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plastic models is freedom. What part to paint is not in the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Dream Crazy color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Inking raises the quality of plastic models...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,by a notch or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This work can be so relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A person? Micro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the pilot, Isamu Dyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:14.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's really good at what he does, \Nbut he's a troublemaker who repeatedly breaks military rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Komukai Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isamu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where are you Isamu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Losing parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's something that happens quite often in the world of plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isamu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isamu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isamu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:49.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where did Isamu-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He'll return eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross Plus YF-19 Battroid mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:17.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san, there's still more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the start of a change in looks, like having a short cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:41.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross Plus YF-19 Fighter mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Double give births, you really get your money's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's still one give birth to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to be punished if you leave a give birth on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:05.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,GERWALK is a mid-conversion mode between the aircraft form and the humanoid-robot form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:07.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's unfinished?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the mid-conversion mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It can land, walk and even hover using it's legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rather than a two-stage transformation \Nmechanism from humanoid to flying mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,don't you think that it's great that they realistically shows the mid-conversion mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:31.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It can be an aircraft. It can also be a humanoid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's this mid-conversion form that holds infinite possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Infinite possibilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at first, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the more I look at it, the more that I like it. GERWALK mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mid-conversion mode is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross Plus YF-19 GERWALK mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:12.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:18.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's eat for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You guys still does that even when you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:20:00.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, even though I'm having such a hard time, when I think that it all comes down to the workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd do anything as long as it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so hard to get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's start a company, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a good idea. \N-What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess we'd have to give it our all during our job hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck?\N-You have no idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not eating that? \N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give it to me then. \N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you smiling? \N-I love petit tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The guilt that I had for not eating all of it is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you guys think about food sharing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:52.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nokoruna started with the two of you laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What an unfinished robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mid-conversion form has infinite charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We were panicking and tried to grow, but
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,this moment right now, might be priceless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Like this GERWALK right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:29.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it... No, I can't see it as a Unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're not going to rush things and we're going to do it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that you're taking the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to what you guys will come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:02.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-kun didn't change what he wanted to do at Dog Run
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and didn't get any investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:10.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess he doesn't want you guys to go trough the pain and suffering that comes afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,From this to Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:34.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:36.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're familiar with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:40.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,
